column1: Wear your attitude on your sleeve with this Big Bag Theory Tote – For Women. This tote bag is made of canvas and hence offers sturdy and rigid support to all your possessions while use. The commodious interiors of this Big Bag Theory Tote – For Women comfortably accommodate the everyday essentials and facilitates instant access to the basic items on the go. Measuring 355.6 x 381 mm in dimension
column2: this satchel is absolutely lightweight and is effortless to carry while use. Besides this
column3: the long and sturdy handle facilitates hassle-free portability. You could pair this Big Bag Theory Tote – For Women with a hip pair of capris and a casual black tee.

column1: It’s funky friday in office but no theme has been attached. You and your colleagues get a text to add a little bit of snazzy fun to your attire. It’s the morning and you are standing in front of your cupboard looking for something to wear. In a Eureka moment
column2: you take out your mint green top with brown pants and pair it with The Big Bag Theory Tote - For Women.

column1: You attire is something that isn’t regular formal wear due to the burst of colour but it is not entirely inappropriate either. As soon as you walk into office
column2: it is compliments galore. Although your’s is not the most funky of outfits it just looked really nice. This tote from The Big Bag Theory is what adds that admirable dose of chutzpah. It is made from canvas which is sturdy apart from being an environmentally conscious choice. Measuring 355.6 x 381 mm in dimension
column3: this tote is made for the woman who is restrained yet reckless.
